WEBVTT

00:00.351 --> 00:02.078
Previously on
<i>The Secret Circle...</i>

00:03.536 --> 00:04.786
Aah!

00:04.788 --> 00:06.288
Cassie.

00:11.044 --> 00:13.128
I'm sorry
about your mom.

00:13.130 --> 00:14.696
Thanks.
Have you seen her yet?

00:14.698 --> 00:16.030
She got in yesterday.

00:16.033 --> 00:17.466
It's ok, Cassie.

00:17.468 --> 00:20.035
We're different.
You're different.

00:20.037 --> 00:23.422
You're a witch. You're
a full blooded, 100% witch.

00:23.424 --> 00:25.206
There's no such thing
as witches and magic.

00:25.208 --> 00:27.208
Are you doing this?

00:27.210 --> 00:29.144
We are.

00:33.983 --> 00:36.651
With her here, we
have real power now.

00:37.904 --> 00:40.439
Each family
has a book,

00:40.441 --> 00:42.858
a journal that lays down each
family line.

00:42.860 --> 00:45.110
A complete circle is 6.

00:45.112 --> 00:46.528
You complete
the circle.

00:46.530 --> 00:47.696
Now we're whole.

00:47.698 --> 00:49.164
You are seriously
messed up.

00:49.166 --> 00:50.732
She's got the gift.

00:50.734 --> 00:53.869
Are you sure you can get
Cassie to do what we need?

00:53.871 --> 00:57.122
The circle will take care of that
without even knowing it.

01:01.427 --> 01:03.762
My sweet Cassie,

01:03.764 --> 01:05.764
I didn't want you
to have this life,

01:05.766 --> 01:09.250
but destiny's not
easy to run from.

01:12.472 --> 01:15.774
You have incredible power
inside you.

01:16.976 --> 01:19.594
People will come for it.

01:19.596 --> 01:21.763
They will come for you.

01:26.435 --> 01:29.538
I hoped that keeping this secret
would keep you safe,

01:29.540 --> 01:31.957
but all I've done
is left you unprotected.

01:35.111 --> 01:36.795
I know how alone
you must feel,

01:36.797 --> 01:38.580
but be careful
who you trust,

01:38.582 --> 01:40.999
even people who
call themselves friends.

01:41.001 --> 01:44.619
Your power is the only thing
that can keep you safe.

